h3-setting-user-attributes-pe8363477.translation:
### 设置用户属性 \{#setting-user-attributes\}

要设置用户属性，请调用 `.updateProfile()` 方法：

```dart showLineNumbers
final builder = AdaptyProfileParametersBuilder()
  ..setEmail("email@email.com")
  ..setPhoneNumber("+18888888888")
  ..setFirstName('John')
  ..setLastName('Appleseed')
  ..setGender(AdaptyProfileGender.other)
  ..setBirthday(DateTime(1970, 1, 3));

try {
  await Adapty().updateProfile(builder.build());
} on AdaptyError catch (adaptyError) {
  // handle the error
} catch (e) {
}
```

h3-custom-user-attributes-pc783daff.translation:
```dart showLineNumbers
try {
  final builder = AdaptyProfileParametersBuilder()
      ..setCustomStringAttribute('value1', 'key1')
      ..setCustomDoubleAttribute(1.0, 'key2');

await Adapty().updateProfile(builder.build());
} on AdaptyError catch (adaptyError) {
// handle the error
} catch (e) {
}
```

要删除已有的键，请使用 `.withRemoved(customAttributeForKey:)` 方法：

h3-custom-user-attributes-p555718df.translation:
```dart showLineNumbers
try {
  final builder = AdaptyProfileParametersBuilder()
    ..removeCustomAttribute('key1')
    ..removeCustomAttribute('key2');

await Adapty().updateProfile(builder.build());
} on AdaptyError catch (adaptyError) {
// handle the error
} catch (e) {
}
```

有时你需要查看之前已设置了哪些自定义属性。为此，请使用 `AdaptyProfile` 对象的 `customAttributes` 字段。
